import { TextField } from "@material-ui/core";
import React from "react";


export function DadosUsuarios () {

    return (
        <>
            <TextField 
                id="email"
                label="Email"
                type="email"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
            <TextField 
                id="senha"
                label="Senha"
                type="password"
                variant="outlined"
                margin="normal"
                fullWidth
            />
        </>
    )
}
